category: Libs
requires: cygwin libsodium0
external-source: libsodium
sdesc: "P(ortable|ackageable) NaCl (development)"
ldesc: "NaCl (pronounced 'salt') is a new easy-to-use high-speed software
library for network communication, encryption, decryption, signatures, etc.

NaCl's goal is to provide all of the core operations needed to build
higher-level cryptographic tools.

Sodium is a portable, cross-compilable, installable, packageable,
API-compatible version of NaCl."
